At Canadian Roofing Company Ltd., we take pride in upholding 
the highest standard of quality & custom workmanship. Mega City Roofing Inc. has attained high standards for re-roofing with many years of experience. Mega City Roofing Inc. has served top-quality products and we strive to be the experts in the business. Our experienced talent and efforts are always continual in our services. We provide information on roofing products and solutions to better our customers requirements.

Mega City Roofing Inc. specializes in re-roofing residential, industrial, and commercial roofs. Even with the best quality roofing systems, your roof is only as good as the quality of the installation. Our excellent product knowledge and highest standards of workmanship assure you of a long-lasting quality roof.

All of our skilled staff is trained in roofing methods, materials, and current Occupational Health and Safety Standards, with many years of actual hands on experience and training. Our service includes inspection, consultation and recommendation of appropriate methods, materials and estimates to resolve our customers individual requirements. We have competitive prices and written guarantee's, customer friendly service and staff. We are fully insured and licensed, our employee's are covered under the WSIB to construct a safe working environment. Call us today and get your FREE estimate inspection and remember a roof is only as good as it's installation. Mega City Roofing Inc. you can trust us for all your roofing needs.

We offer shingle roofing and flat roofing services, plus low-slope, cedar and slate roofing.
 
Our goal is to ensure each and every customer has the security of a job well done. 
That's why we stress superior products, superior workmanship and superior service. 

Our motto, "We've got your peace of mind covered," guides all our activities and we work hard to live up to it! 

Please visit our website at www.lucsroofing.com
416-222-2672

Our skilled, experienced craftsmen, aided by the reliable products, can accurately assess your roofing situation and expedite any job quickly and to your full satisfaction. 

We are dedicated to providing quality, professional installation and service commitment with fair prices. For your protection we are fully insured, bonded and licensed, and are proud members of the Better Business Bureau. profile:
John Stewart, owner of J. STEWART ROOFING Ltd, has been installing roofs for the Toronto area homes and small businesses for over twenty five years. John is an experienced roofer having started roofing at a very young age he learned the basics of roofing and gradually became proficient in both shingling and then flat roofing. These two very different types of roofs require a different knowledge base and a real understanding of this can only be gained through actual hands-on work, so that one can see exactly how the materials work together and why.  

Flat roofs are particularly tricky to do and have become a specialty for J. Stewart Roofing Ltd. (For further details check out the newspaper article from the Toronto Star on this website. It is vital to gain real knowledge of the materials & techniques to not get stuck in just one way of doing things and stop there. Larry and John know how important it is to always keep up with the new roofing materials being invented and how they actually work in the field. In this way they have gained a greater library of knowledge on which to draw from, enabling them to know what combination of materials best for each unique customerâ€™s job are presented to them. 

We specialize in all areas of roofing:

Shingle Roofs 	Flat Roofs 	Repairs & Maintenance
Asphalt 	Modified Bitumen

profile:
Vassa Enterprises offers homeowners a specialized one on one approach from beginning to end.  Owner and operator Tony Kavai will make sure you choose the right product at the right price.  Not having a sales team allows Tony to know first hand exactly what your expectations are and effectively make sure those expectations are delivered on.  Managing the sale himself also allows Tony to save you the hidden costs of commissions usually paid out to sales people, this he happily passes on to his customers.   To learn more about our product visit www.gerardusa.com

***
 
We offer you a quality stone coated metal roofing product manufactured by GERARD roofing technologies. This outstanding roofing material carries a limited lifetime warranty, which is not only transferable but also non-prorated. Whether your building is a residential house, apartment, commercial building, community house or a church, GERARD roofing tiles, shakes or shingles are the ultimate solution for your roofing need.
Gerard Stone Coated Steel, â€˜Canyon Shakeâ€™ metal roof tile profile offers the best of all worlds for customers who want the look of wood shake with the strength and security of steel metal roofing.  Unlike wood shake, our premium stone coated steel roofing tiles will never need the costly maintenance, upkeep and replacement that natural wood shake roofs require.

***

Natural wood shake is not water proof, and needs to be maintained / treated for mold and fungus growth, and relies heavily on a vapor barrier underlayment to protect your roof deck. Our stone coated steel tiles are waterproof, and are categorized as a "dry under-deck" roofing system, keeping your roof deck dry year round under the most testing of conditions. With Gerard's stone coated tiles you won't need to treat for mold and fungus, and over the decades, your shake style roof will continue to look beautiful while delivering the best protection, as the day it was installed!

profile:
Meet the Independent Roof Inspection Team Servicing the GTA
At Independent Roof Inspection Services, we were salesman, estimators, and roofers. Roofing was what we did. We all climbed up ladders, loaded building materials and made a mess. However, when we were done, the property was always thoroughly cleaned up and the roofs didnâ€™t leak anymore. We had a lot of satisfied customers but after years of being roofers, it was time for us to finally try something new. Because owner Dave Baughn had seen many mistakes and bad contractors throughout his years in roofing, he decided something needed to be done â€“ hence, Independent Roof Inspection Services.

Independent Roof Inspection Services is not a roofing company offering to do inspections on the side. As an independent roof inspector, we offer our inspection services at affordable rates to homeowners, property managers, real estate companies, developers and landlords of residential, commercial and industrial properties across the Greater Toronto Area. Our detailed roof inspection reports describe the existing waterproofing, its age and condition, and all of your available options. While you may need to completely replace your roof, other times you might not need a new roof at all. Sometimes a repair or a partial re-roof may suffice. 
We inspect Commercial, Residential and Industrial properties and provide Project Management services, overseeing  flat and shingle re-roofing projects including custom new-build homes.

profile:
My name is Harold Spissinger and I have been roofing for 31 years. I have been on the roof doing the actual work for this time and am on the roof for most jobs. My crew of men have been with me for over twenty years ( same guys ) and they are all family men. I have working for me, men who are dedicated professionals who care about the work they do.
     My goal is to provide the best value for the money as I deliver roofing systems done in accordance with the building code, manufacturers specifications(all of which I am extremely familiar) and all the by-laws. This ensures a roofing system which performs very well over long periods of time. All of my men are trained in Fall Protection and have their up-to-date certs by the Ministry of Labour.
products:
SHINGLES: Certainteed,Owens Corning, BP, IKO, GAF.
FLAT ROOFING:modified Bitumen by IKO 
CEDAR:Cedar Bureau approved products
services: Shingle roofing, flat roofing, complete skylight installations including carpentry and interior drywall work, repairs to existing roofs, rafter replacing and repairs including re-sloping of ponding flat roofs, new deck on flat roofs, insulation with the roofs either blown in or baton or styrofoam, all types of metal work including flashings using steel or copper or galvanized metal, aluminum work including gutters, down pipes, siding (siding of vinyl,composite,wood etc.), decks for flat roofs in pressure treated wood, cedar or composite materials.
specialities: Re-raftering collapsing roofs(all carpentry work). Experts at skylight installations (new or repairing existing), 30 year flat roofing systems, 30 year to 50 year shingled roofing systems. Ventilation systems to handle condensation issues. Re-sloping or ponding flat roofs. Termite roofing projects done with termite companys ( I am licenced to spray the roof when its open etc )
payment_method: check, cash or email transfer. NO credit cards

Our aim is to provide the highest levels of workmanship in our project implementation, but also to provide the best possible client experience in the industry. At Sum-it Roofing Inc., reliability, integrity and efficiency is our motto. Our fully licensed and insured commercial and residential roofers offer A+ roofing repairs or replacement at a fair and competitive price. We take pride in our work as we install the optimum roofing system to meet your budget. We are confident in our work that's why we are able to provide a 10yrs workmanship warranty. 
We strongly believe that a good roof comprise of more than just new shingles. Although it's important to select a durable roof shingles from a reputable manufacturer with a good warranty, Its equally important to have a proper underlayment paired with a high performance Ice & water membrane.

profile:
1 2 3 Roofing is a leader in roofing systems application and client care. Our aim is to provide the highest levels of workmanship in our project implementation, but also to provide the best possible client experience in the industry. Balancing those two aspects of our work, while maintaining value pricing, is what sets 1 2 3 Roofing contractors apart.

We hold the accreditation of CertainTeed Shingle Master with CertainTeed St. Gobain, the world leader in shingle manufacturing. The stringent guidelines mandated by CertainTeed in the application of their product allows us to maintain the exceedingly high standards we are reputed for as roofers. 

123 Roofing services South Western Ontario, from Kitchener/Waterloo through, Hamilton, Halton, North York, Vaughan and into Barrie with sloped and flat roofing system replacements, eavestrough, skylight, shingles and attic insulation and ventilation work being our specialities.

Call today and one of our roofing systems consultants will be happy to help!

We offer Free Roofing Estimates, quality service from the removal of old roofing, repair of sub roofing and the install of new shingles to protect your home from ice damage & the elements and give your home the designer look you always wanted!

One of the latest ongoing trends in roofing styles is the Architectural style of shingles these are reminiscent of slate and cedar shingles without the high cost of those materials. For homeowners who want extra durability and protection, select IKO`s Cambridge premium architectural shingles. Cambridge combines beauty with contemporary strength. Manufactured in a larger size to offer more exposure and create a high definition ''shake'' look for your roof, these popular shingles are versatile and easy to maintain and come in a myriad of colors that can suit any home. The Cambridge shingle features an algae resistant granule.

Marathon 25 and 25 AR shingles are a time-tested, traditional three-tab shingle. Traditional 3-tab design shingles. Available in a wide range of colors, the Marathon 25 shingle instantly makes your home a classic. Offering excellent reliability and supported by a proven track record, these shingles are at the top of their class in terms of performance and value. Marathon 25 AR shingles feature an algae resistant granule and a limited 25-Year Warranty. When it`s time to choose or replace your roof, look no further for a shingle that offers unbeatable protection and value

profile: At Skyluxe our desire is to challenge the status quo within the Toronto roofing industry. We demand perfection in everything that we do, that is what keeps us going, that is what inspires us and ultimately, what makes us feel alive. Our passion for excellence radiates from our employees in a unique, contagious and addictive manner and it will be easily visible from the initial roof consultation.  We are professional and we care.  We will walk you through the entire process of the roof replacement/repair and offer recommendations which will fit your budget.  You will receive a professional and detailed proposal with photos which will describe all roof issues and remedies for your unique situation.  Once the project is confirmed, your project will be placed in the schedule.  During the project set-up phase your home will be completely protected before work begins.  The project will be executed until completion. Lastly, a final walk-through with you, to address any deficiencies or questions is conducted along with a final site cleanup.

profile:
Protect your home from damage caused by the elements with roofing services by Panda Roofing. We provide professional roof repair and maintenance in GTA and surrounding areas of the GTA for local home and business owners. Our experienced team is committed to delivering exceptional workmanship using top quality roofing materials, and we are fully licensed for your protection and peace of mind.
At Panda Roofing, we do a lot more than roof repair. Call on us to repair, maintain, and install a range of components to your
roofing system, including skylights, Eavestroughs , gutters, chimneys, leaf guards and more. Additionally, we provide professional trapping, sink repair, cleaning, and replacement, tank cleaning, repair and installation, and more.
As a locally owned roofing company, Liscensed and insured, we ensure our quality and service to a high degree.
For over 15 years, our workers has been travelling to every corner in Greater Toronto Area to serve everyone in need, we guarantee your satisfaction on our price, our work and service.
Our commitment is to provide the best service with a better material at a lower price.
Free Estimate please Call: 647-296-7881    [Roy]

At Hamkar roofing, Our mission is to provide quality, on time and affordable Roofing service. We follow all safety regulations and only use industry approved materials.

Our team at Hamkar roofing consists of Experienced and Professional Roofers from Greater Toronto Area with a fifteen (15) years warranty on materials we use.

Our Services include New construction roofing as well as complete replacement of old roof and repairs and maintenance of all residential and commercial roofing with options such as Shingle Roofing, Flat Roofing, Cedar Roofing, Slate Roofing, Skylights and more.

profile:
Since 2006, Magno Contractor's Inc began from the hard work of its founder, and has evolved to become a full service roofing company that covers residential and commercial customers all throughout the Greater Toronto Area. 
We commit to provide quality installations and repairs with our skilled and experienced workers. We offer shingle and flat roofing services, and we also deal with cedar and slate roofing. With 14+ years of experience, we want to ensure every customer the security that the job will get done. But also, we want for the customer to feel satisfied with our work.

Your Flat Roofing Contactor Experts
Chicago Flat Roof Company is a family-owned commercial, industrial and residential roofing company, proudly serving the city of Chicago IL and the surrounding communities. We specialize in roofing installation, roof repair and roof maintenance. Our specialty techniques include TPO roofing and EDPM roofing. We even perform rooftop services such as roof snow removal and gutter repair. Throughout the years, our success has been well earned and is a result of our commitment to providing the highest quality services available in the roofing industry today. Equipped with the latest technological tools, and our highly skilled team, we have consistently demonstrated the ability to take on projects of any size. Contact Chicago Flat Roof Company today to take care of all of your roofing needs. Visit our website for more information.

profile:
5/5 stars Roof Repair or Maintenance Verified Review

We are a new company Established 2014. Far from new to the home improvement business, w/ 18 years experience, we can take on all your home improvement needs. Proudly serving Worcester and Middlesex counties. We made it our goal to learn everything so our customers do not have to get referred else where to take on there needs, we know how it is when you find someone you can trust, honest and reliable. The last thing you want to hear is we are going to have to refer you to another company. We pride ourselves with Excellent quality work. 

I gotta say...Curtis and his twin brother responded quickly -- they quoted fairly...and simply did the work promptly...the leaks...are gone - and it rained that very evening with harsh wind - mission accomplished! 

When they were done - they looked me in the eye and said - if there was ever a problem in the future - to call them back immediately and they'd respond - no questions asked and resolve it promptly.

Charming, Professional, Decent - Salt-of-the-earth, Honest Hardworking and Motivated...

What more can you ask for?

Two leaks expertly repaired within hours.

Better than average...Nope...Outstanding!

I will absolutely use these guys again - Curtis and his twin brother Rob - aren't "nicky new kids"...they are solid in both knowledge and talent. Well done!

Cheers to you and your company!

Brett Linton
Lancaster, MA

Brett L. on February 25, 2016
5/5 stars Skylights Verified Review


I recently had three very old and tired skylights replaced in my family room by Better Home Improvement. The company owners are brothers who take great pride in their work and in carrying on a long family tradition of delivering excellent results for their customers. My experience lived up to their reputation. They did extensive traveling to locate the right skylights and had them installed in a few hours. They even did some extra wood detail work around the openings to accommodate the new design of the modern windows. When the work was complete, they left everything immaculate and even vacuumed.They were very responsive throughout the process and had competitive pricing.

Patty N. on February 7, 2016
5/5 stars


Better Home Improvement put a roof on my house. The job was done in a timely fashion, great quality, and they left the yard as clean as they found it. I would highly recommend Better Home Improvement.

Ann M. on November 7, 2015
5/5 stars


Better Home Improvement did our roof and also replaced our soffits! They did a wonderful job- very professional and very courteous and hard working! I would highly recommend them for your next project.

Jeanne T. on November 1, 2015
5/5 stars


I heard about BHI from a friend and called them to get an estimate on a new roof for my house. They were over 20% less than the nearest roof estimate that I received (I had called 3 other roofing companies). They were there within 2 weeks and they finished the job in 3 days, cleaned up all debris and the roof looks amazing! That was in May and since then they have built a deck for my best friend, roofed my brother's house, sided and roofed a commercial building that I own and they have just finished a foundation repair and are adding a large addition to a rental house of mine. Their work is great and they always follow MA building code and their rates are difficult to beat on any project. I don't even bother comparing estimates anymore because I am confident that Curt, Rob and the crew will always give me a great job at an honest price. Feel free to contact me and I will personally show you the work that they have done for me.

wayne b. on October 29, 2015
5/5 stars


I have used Better Home Improvement for several projects. I think they did a great job and were professional, reliable and reasonable.
Cary Orlandi
President Millbrook Homes

Cary O. on October 19, 2015

profile:
ROOF REPAIRS INCLUDE : 
*Shingle Type:________[] 25 years [] 30 years [] lifetime 

Colour:__________ 

*Remove old shingles 

*Inspect plywood and replace and damaged ones 

*Install 3feet of ice&water protection on perimeter of roof 

*Install 29 gauge aluminum flashing in all valleys 

*Install ice&water protection in critical areas where required 

*Replace all rubber flanges 

*Replace all air vents 

*Re-fasten and re-caulk flashing 

*Clean eavestroughs and remove nails from surrounding areas 

*All garbage is collected and disposed 

*Install shingles professionally&Ten years labour warranty after the work is finished 

Upgrade:Install ice&water protection/felt paper on whole roof 
Install turbine vents&ventilation tower vents 

We will use the shingle types include: (Upgrade to IKO /BP/GAF,TIMBERLINE /Landmark Certanateed/Owens Corning/Lifetime shingles/30 years shingles) 


** Roof Repair Services ** 

* Animal Damage Repair 
* Shingle Repair 
* Chimney Demolition 
* Gutter (Eavestrough) Repair & Replacement 
* Flashing /Siding/Soffit Repair 
* Skylight Isolation 
* Valley Replacement 
* Leaf Guard 
* Vent Replacement

With 15+ years of industry experience, you can depend on Puma Commercial Roofing for expert commercial, industrial, and residential roofing services. Our company specializes in roof repair, installation, commercial roof restoration, maintenance programs, and more. Based in Arden, NC, we proudly serve customers in the following areas: Spartanburg (SC), Florance (SC), Rock Hill (SC), Columbia (SC), Greenville (SC), Charlotte (NC), Shelby (NC), Hendersonville (NC), Ashville (NC), Arden (NC), and surrounding communities.

Whether you require localized repair services, ongoing maintenance, or a complete roof replacement, the specialists at Puma Commercial Roofing can help. A licensed & insured company, Puma Commercial Roofing can professionally handle all of your residential, commercial, and industrial roofing needs.

profile:
Thermaco Engineering are roof consultants in southern Ontario offering inspection of both residential, commercial and industrial properties. We have over thirty years experience in the inspection of shingle roofs, slate, metal roof panels, wood shakes. We are recognized by the courts for assisting you in litigation cases where you need to sue a roofing contractor or you need mediation to get your roof system in good shape and dry. We also inspect attics for adequate ventilation and insulation conditions. If you have problems with squirrels and other animals you need to replace your insulation. For advice on helping solve your ice damming problems, early shingle loss visit our website at www.thermacoeng.com. We are not roof contractors we are independent roof inspectors and professional consulting engineers. Some of our clients include large property managers, 
condominiums, Toronto Community Housing Corporation. We have managed projects up to $ 1 million for replacing roofs over large townhouse complexes as well. If you need a professional report go to the professionals not the firms with 1 or two years experience. Unlike our competitors we have thirty years experience in infrared testing as well.
name: Thermaco Engineering Services (1986) Ltd.
